			"text": "via integer linear programming . <S>",
			"relation": "manner-means"
		},
		{
			"id": 12,
			"parent": 5,
			"text": "Evaluation on PDTB shows significant performance improvements of our constituent-based approach over the best state-of-the-art system . <S>",
			"relation": "evaluation"
		},
		{
			"id": 13,
